com.gedder.gedderalarm.model

Class AlarmClock

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gedder.gedderalarm.model.AlarmClock
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class AlarmClock
extends Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    An alarm clock class encapsulating all data for both a typical alarm clock and the specialized Gedder alarm clock.
